title: spamphishing
extract: uk ​ /ˈfɪʃ.ɪŋ/ us ​ /ˈfɪʃ.ɪŋ/ an attempt to trick someone into giving information over the internet or by email that would allow someone else to take money from them , for example by taking money out of their bank account. Fraud & corruption. baksheesh. blackmail.
